categories: Category:Articles that are known by a nickname

nodes.text: A pilot served in the Resistance during its war with the First Order. In 35 ABY, this pilot served as under the callsign Delta Leader in the Battle of Exegol, where the pilot was shot down and killed.
The Resistance pilot using the callsign "Delta Leader" was briefly mentioned in the 2019 sequel trilogy film Star Wars: Episode IX The Rise of Skywalker.
